{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "石破天被抛入船舱，误闯阿绣被窝，与同样因练功走火而无法动弹的阿绣、史婆婆相识。丁不四挟持祖孙欲返碧螺岛，途中与石破天斗口、比招，反被石破天凭浑厚内力和丁珰所授擒拿手制住。其后史婆婆看出石破天内功深厚，指点他运使罗汉伏魔功，为自己缓缓通脉。三人脱船落水后逃到紫烟岛暂避，阿绣温柔体贴，史婆婆则刚烈尖刻，对丁氏兄弟恨意甚深。石破天在救人、对掌和疗伤之间，逐渐显出心地纯善与内功潜力，也与阿绣祖孙建立起初步信任。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "女子",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "什么人？你⋯⋯你怎么⋯⋯",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真动不得啊，你们瞧，我给人抓了灵台穴，又拿了悬枢穴，全身又给绑得结结实实，要移动半分也动不了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "姑娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "什么太太的？我是姑娘，我也动不得。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锯不得，锯不得！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "姑娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "奶奶，我拔刀子也没力气。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_a_xiu",
      "text": "你没力气拔刀子，那再好没有了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来老太太和小姑娘都练内功走火，动弹不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_a_xiu",
      "text": "小翠，我在船头等你。你伏在舱里想施暗算，我可不上你当。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_a_xiu",
      "text": "姑娘，你奶奶坐起来啦。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "你快进来救人。老太太要投江自尽了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_a_xiu",
      "text": "阿绣，端阳节早过，你却在被窝中藏了一只大粽子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "阿绣",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "不是的，他是外边飞进来的，不⋯⋯不是我藏的。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "她既不愿去，你怎能勉强人家？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "要你放什么狗屁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "你也要杀？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "丁不四的心意，天下有谁猜得中？你以为我要杀你，我就偏偏不杀。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "老爷子，你这手功夫厉害得很，那叫什么名堂？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "不可动粗！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "连一个浑小子也⋯⋯也⋯⋯也⋯⋯",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "你再多说一句，我立时将你掷入江心。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "江湖上人人都说，丁氏双雄，一是英雄，一是狗熊！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "几时有这句话了？定是你捏造出来的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "你不在十万招之内将他打败，你就拜他⋯⋯拜他⋯⋯",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "你就拜他为师！你要说这句话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "就算你没输，那么你让他在你大椎穴上拍一掌瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "好端端地，我为什么要给他打？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "他妈的，你不会，我来教你。你瞧仔细了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "下面的我不会了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "我原说不用比啦，算你赢就是了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "错了！不是这样拆法。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "老太太，你⋯⋯你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "阿绣",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "这位大哥，我奶奶怎么了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "阿绣",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你说我奶奶⋯⋯已经⋯⋯已经死了？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_a_xiu",
      "text": "姑娘，原来你也这么好看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_a_xiu",
      "text": "对不起！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "好，我来教你。你将内息存于丹田，感到有一股热烘烘的暖气了，是不是？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你心中想着，让那暖气通到手少阳三焦经的经脉上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "这招拆法我教过你，不算不讲理罢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "这一招我也教过你的，总不能说我耍无赖欺侮小辈了罢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "就算学得跟你一模一样，又有什么用？他不学你的武功，便能将你打败。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "少年，你过来，别去理他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "他会不会吐血？可别伤了他。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "不会的。你良心倒好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "大粽子，这招逆水行舟要打过来啦！那是我教过你的，可别忘了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 589
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "错了！不是这样拆法。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 593,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "小翠，到碧螺岛啦，你们祖孙两位，连同大粽子一起，都请上去盘桓盘桓。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老妇",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "不去，我宁死也不踏上你的鬼岛一步。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "上去住几天打什么紧？你是我家贵客。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 655,
      "line_end": 655
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "好啦，你可放我们下来了，这里是紫烟岛，离那老怪居住之处不远，须得防他过来啰唣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 699,
      "line_end": 699
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "是，是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我如不是练功走火，区区丁不三何足道哉！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "阿绣",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "奶奶，此刻你老人家功力未复，暂且避一避丁氏兄弟的锋头。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "阿绣",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "奶奶，过去的事情，又提它干么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 723,
      "line_end": 723
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "辛苦你了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "我又不累，咱们便把其余经脉都打通了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "小子胡说八道，我是和阿绣同练无妄神功以致走火。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 751
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到底我是谁，我⋯⋯我实在说不上来⋯⋯",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 777,
      "line_end": 777
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你不肯说就不说好了，偏有这么啰哩啰唆的一大套鬼话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "阿绣",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_po",
      "text": "奶奶，人家不愿说，总是有什么难言之隐，咱们也不用问了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 779,
      "line_end": 779
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "史婆婆",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "大粽子，今晚你睡在外面守着，可不许进来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
